  "rdfs:comment": {
    "de": [
      "Am Fuße des Waldmassivs La Loube erwartet Sie das Château des Chaberts, ein altes Weingut mit 250 Hektar Land, von denen 30 Hektar mit Weinreben bepflanzt sind. Die Lage ist bemerkenswert, der Weinberg umschließt die Bastide und die Wirtschaftsgebäude."
    ],
    "en": [
      "Château des Chaberts is situated in the heart of Provence at the foothills of the Loube mountain range. Il is built on a remarkable south facing site of a Roman settlement. It is surrounded by hills in the form of a horse shoe which provides shelter from the prevailing winds whilst a continual gentle breeze gives protection from the spring frosts and summer heat. It is situated at an altitude of 365 metres and comprises of 650 acres with 65 in vines. It has stony, chalky, clay soil and benefits from a micro-climate. The appellation is Coteaux Varois en Provence and has been organic since 2017.\r\nChâteau des Chaberts wines are typical of the region. They are made with great respect for tradition and with constant attention to quality - attested year after year by the many awards at Paris, Macon, Vinalies, Guide Hachette,..."
    ],
    "it": [
      "Ai piedi del massiccio forestale della Loube, vi attende lo Château des Chaberts, un'antica proprietà vinicola di 250 ettari, di cui 30 a vigneto. Il sito è notevole, il vigneto circonda la bastide e gli edifici della fattoria."
    ],
    "fr": [
      "Au pied du massif forestier qu'est la Loube, le Château des Chaberts, vieille propriété viticole de 250 hectares dont 30 hectares en vignes, vous attend. Le site est remarquable, le vignoble enserre la bastide et les bâtiments d'exploitation."
    ],
    "es": [
      "Al pie del macizo forestal que es el Loube, le espera el Château des Chaberts, una antigua propiedad vitícola de 250 hectáreas, 30 de las cuales son viñedos. El sitio es notable, el viñedo rodea la bastida y los edificios de la granja."
    ],
    "nl": [
      "Aan de voet van het bosmassief van de Loube ligt het Château des Chaberts, een oud wijndomein van 250 hectare, waarvan 30 wijngaarden, op u te wachten. De site is opmerkelijk, de wijngaard omringt de bastide en de boerderijgebouwen."
    ]
  },
